data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 4-beds, 2-baths residence boasts a perfect blend of style, comfort, and natural beauty. Situated with a serene pond view, a brick front facade, and meticulously manicured landscaping, this property offers a unique and inviting living experience. Step inside & you're greeted by the warmth of beautiful laminate flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the entire home. The spacious living areas are filled with natural light, creating an inviting ambiance for gatherings & relaxation. Primary Suite bath just remodeled with luxury features so you can pamper yourself. All bedrooms are generously sized. Located in a desirable community, close to parks, schools & shopping.Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Welcome Home!
